title: Petition/Application Was Rejected For Insufficient Funds
body: On March 10, 2021, we rejected your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190086436 because your filing fee was returned by your financial institution for insufficient funds. Any previously assigned priority or processing date is no longer applicable. If you wish to still pursue the benefit, you must file a new application or petition and submit a new fee filing fee. If you need assistance, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you change your mailing address, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Expedite Request Denied
body: On March 11, 2021, we denied your request for expedited processing of your I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190086437. We do not believe, based on a review of your request, that your case meets one or more of the expedite criteria and otherwise merits expedited processing. We review all expedite requests on a case-by-case basis, and we grant them at the discretion of the director. Information regarding the USCIS expedite policy, including the expedite criteria, is available at www.uscis.gov/forms/expedite-criteria. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Petition/Application Was Rejected For Insufficient Funds
body: On March 11, 2021, we rejected your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190086666 because your filing fee was returned by your financial institution for insufficient funds. Any previously assigned priority or processing date is no longer applicable. If you wish to still pursue the benefit, you must file a new application or petition and submit a new fee filing fee. If you need assistance, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you change your mailing address, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
